txt.en: <rgb=#00e4ff>This quest has been restored for Legendary Servers!</rgb>\n\nThe markings on this marsh-fly queen are unlike any you have heard of before. Surely, someone at the Hunter's Lodge would care to see it.
'Well done, [placeholder]! This is a most peculiar find!'
You've slain a most peculiar-looking marsh-fly queen.
Show the marsh-fly queen to someone at the Hunter's Lodge
The Hunter's Lodge is to the east of Archet.\n\nYou should take the carcass of the marsh-fly queen to the Hunter's Lodge to see if anyone has more information for you.
